query:
INSERT INTO tutor_profiles (
  userId, 
  bio, 
  qualifications, 
  subjects, 
  gradeLevels, 
  hourlyRate, 
  yearsOfExperience, 
  approvalStatus,
  isActive
) 
SELECT 
  id,
  'Experienced educator specializing in course administration and tutoring',
  'Course Administrator with teaching certification',
  '["Mathematics","Science","English"]',
  '["Elementary (K-5)","Middle School (6-8)","High School (9-12)"]',
  '45.00',
  5,
  'pending',
  1
FROM users 
WHERE email = 'courseadmin@edkonnect.com';
